                         <td align="left" valign="top"><p><span class="towns">Michael Jording, MD </span><br />
                            Michael is a practicing family physician in Newcastle, WY who has been very involved in furthering rural healthcare initiatives in Wyoming. He has been very active for over 20 years in providing medical education to medical students, residents, and other healthcare professionals, particularly through the Casper Family Medicine Residency and the WWAMI medical student education program. Most recently, Michael served as president of the <a href="/http://www.wyomed.org/" target="_blank">Wyoming Medical Society</a>, and continues to be a member of the WMS Board of Trustees. </p></td>
